    "long_instructions": "## Computational Thinking \r\n## Part 2 - Refine Your Plan\r\n\r\nUse the chatbot to apply **abstraction** by focusing only on the most important tasks in your event plan.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n- Tell the chatbot what event you're planning.\r\n- Share the list of tasks you’ve already written.\r\n- Ask the chatbot to help you simplify your plan by identifying the most essential tasks and removing anything unnecessary.\r\n\r\n**Example Prompt:**\r\n- **Refine:** *I'm planning a school spirit week. My task list includes picking a theme for each day, designing flyers, creating a playlist, organizing a pep rally, ordering decorations, and buying snacks. Which of these are the most important, and which could I combine or remove?*",
